ext-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i t\u1ef1 h&agrave;o v\u1ec1 c&aacute;ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng b\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c&aacute;c ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng uy t&iacute;n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2011 \u0111\u1ebfn nay v&agrave; li&ecirc;n t\u1ee5c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c&aacute;c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh \u0111&agrave;o t\u1ea1o nh\u1eb1m n&acirc;ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c v&agrave; khuy\u1ebfn kh&iacute;ch s\u1ef1 tham gia t&iacute;ch c\u1ef1c v&agrave;o c&aacute;c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Caravelle Saigon cho h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh ti\u1ebfp theo kh&ocirc;ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l&agrave; ch\u1ecdn n\u01a1i l\u01b0u tr&uacute;; b\u1ea1n \u0111ang tham gia c&ugrave;ng ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i tr&ecirc;n m\u1ed9t h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh \u0111\u1ea7y &yacute; ngh\u0129a h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai xanh h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 184px;top: 55.4801px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48g0dtib{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 50px;} .ffb-id-48g0dtic{ text-align: center;}.ffb-id-48g0dtig{ padding-right: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}@media (min-width:768px) { .ffb-id-48g0dtig{ padding-right: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}}@media (min-width:992px) { .ffb-id-48g0dtig{ padding-right: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}}@media (min-width:1200px) { .ffb-id-48g0dtig{ padding-right: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}}.ffb-id-48g0dtig ,.ffb-id-48g0dtig:before,.ffb-id-48g0dtig:after,.ffb-id-48g0dtig *,.ffb-id-48g0dtig *:before,.ffb-id-48g0dtig *:after{ color: #797979 !important;}.ffb-id-48g0dtig{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48g0dtig:before,.ffb-id-48g0dtig