luid fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row fg-row-no-gutter   \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-7jo6q60l fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-7jo6q60n fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Earth-Hour-2024-web1.jpg\" alt=\"Earth-Hour-2024-web1\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-7jo6q60o fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-7jo6q60q fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Earth-Hour-2024-web3.jpg\" alt=\"Earth-Hour-2024-web3\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-7jo6q60r fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-7jo6q60t fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Earth-Hour-2024-web2.jpg\" alt=\"Earth-Hour-2024-web2\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-7jo6q60u fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-7jo6q610 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CARAVELLE T\u1ed4 CH\u1ee8C \"RUN FOR GREEN\" H\u01af\u1edeNG \u1ee8NG GI\u1edc TR&Aacute;I \u0110\u1ea4T 2024<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">V&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 16 th&aacute;ng 3 n\u0103m 2024, Caravelle Associates v&agrave; Qu\u1ea3n l&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n \u0111&atilde; c&ugrave;ng nhau tham gia s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n &ldquo;RUN FOR GREEN&rdquo;, nh\u1eb1m n&acirc;ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c v&agrave; \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 th&ocirc;ng \u0111i\u1ec7p r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed7i h&agrave;nh \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1ecf h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec1u c&oacute; th\u1ec3 c&oacute; t&aacute;c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111&aacute;ng k\u1ec3.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eb1m g&oacute;p ph\u1ea7n v&agrave;o s\u1ef1 ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng c\u1ee7a qu\u1ed1c gia, ph&ugrave; h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l&agrave; \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c NetZero trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">_____________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CARAVELLE SAIGON H\u01af\u1edeNG \u1ee8NG GI\u1edc TR&Aacute;I \u0110\u1ea4T 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Caravelle Saigon s&aacute;t c&aacute;nh c&ugrave;ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng to&agrave;n c\u1ea7u trong cam k\u1ebft b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v&agrave; gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh&iacute; th\u1ea3i carbon. T\u1eeb 8h30 t\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebfn 21h30, Caravelle s\u1ebd t\u1eaft to&agrave;n b\u1ed9 \u0111&egrave;n \u1edf m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n, c&aacute;c nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, qu&aacute;n bar c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 b\u1eefa t\u1ed1i v&agrave; \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi &aacute;nh n\u1ebfn. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c\u0169ng m\u1eddi c&aacute;c v\u1ecb kh&aacute;ch trong nh&agrave; tham gia b\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch t\u1eaft \u0111&egrave;n v&agrave; c&aacute;c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb kh&ocirc;ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong gi\u1edd n&agrave;y.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n Gi\u1edd Tr&aacute;i \u0111\u1ea5t h&agrave;ng n\u0103m n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng ch\u1ec9 t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0ng cho m\u1ed9t h&agrave;nh \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng; n&oacute; \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho m\u1ed9t quan \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v&igrave; hy v\u1ecdng v&agrave; h&agrave;nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v&igrave; h&agrave;nh tinh n&agrave;y. L&agrave; Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng v&agrave; l&agrave; Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u ti&ecirc;n \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u EarthCheck Platinum, Caravelle Saigon t\u1ef1 h&agrave;o ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng tham gia Gi\u1edd Tr&aacute;i \u0111\u1ea5t, n&ecirc;u b\u1eadt cam k\u1ebft kh&ocirc;ng ng\u1eebng c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">_____________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\u0110&Egrave;N LED TRONG PH&Ograve;NG<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i r\u1ea5t vui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia s\u1ebb th&ecirc;m nh\u1eefng s&aacute;ng ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200bxanh trong c&aacute;c ph&ograve;ng ngh\u1ec9 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c&aacute;c ph&ograve;ng hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111&egrave;n LED, thay th\u1ebf c&aacute;c b&oacute;ng \u0111&egrave;n truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng ti&ecirc;u t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110i-\u1ed1t ph&aacute;t quang (LED) l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng ngh\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfu s&aacute;ng ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay, c&oacute; th\u1ec3 gi&uacute;p gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee9c ti&ecirc;u th\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec7n cho chi\u1ebfu s&aacute;ng t\u1edbi 80% v&agrave; c&oacute; tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cao h\u01a1n 25 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi \u0111&egrave;n s\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1t.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">C&ugrave;ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng ch&iacute;nh m\u1edbi n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi c\u1ee7a gi\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea1n, c&aacute;c ph&ograve;ng c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111&egrave;n c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf l\u1ed1i v&agrave;o s\u1ebd b\u1eadt \u0111&egrave;n khi ph&aacute;t hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng n&agrave;o v&agrave; t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eaft \u0111&egrave;n sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r&atilde;i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfu s&aacute;ng LED trong c&aacute;c ph&ograve;ng v&agrave; t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c&aacute;c khu v\u1ef1c M\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n nh&agrave; s\u1ebd t&aacute;c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111&aacute;ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn c&aacute;c s&aacute;ng ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200bti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i cho n\u0103m 2020 v&agrave; h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">_____________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>H&Agrave;NH \u0110\u1ed8NG XANH CHO M\u1ed8T M&Ocirc;I TR\u01af\u1edcNG B\u1ec0N V\u1eeeNG H\u01a0N<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">N\u0103m 2019, Caravelle Saigon d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong c&aacute;c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh n&acirc;ng c\u1ea5p v&agrave;o n\u0103m 2020. N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp ti&ecirc;n phong th\u1ef1c h&agrave;nh xanh. \u0110\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn b\u1ea1ch kim EarthCheck v&agrave;o n\u0103m 2020, n&oacute; tr\u1edf th&agrave;nh t&agrave;i s\u1ea3n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam c&oacute; danh hi\u1ec7u n&agrave;y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">C&aacute;c ph&ograve;ng ngh\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t&acirc;n trang l\u1ea1i c&oacute; h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111&egrave;n LED ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v&agrave; c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 l\u1eafp k&iacute;nh hai l\u1edbp nh\u1eb1m gi\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v&agrave;o \u0111i\u1ec1u h&ograve;a kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; v&agrave; t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c&aacute;ch nhi\u1ec7t. Ngo&agrave;i ra, c&aacute;c ti\u1ec7n nghi trong ph&ograve;ng nh\u01b0 m&aacute;y c\u1ea1o r&acirc;u, b&agrave;n ch\u1ea3i \u0111&aacute;nh r\u0103ng v&agrave; l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u tr\u1ea5u l&uacute;a m&igrave; c&oacute; th\u1ec3 ph&acirc;n h\u1ee7y sinh h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute;nh c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i l&agrave; truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n, gia \u0111&igrave;nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v&agrave; kh&aacute;ch &aacute;p d\u1ee5ng c&aacute;c bi\u1ec7n ph&aacute;p th\u1ef1c h&agrave;nh c&oacute; &yacute; th\u1ee9c sinh th&aacute;i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh&iacute; th\u1ea3i carbon. Khi ch&uacute;ng ta h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u0103m 2024 \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, Caravelle v\u1eabn ki&ecirc;n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi cam k\u1ebft m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c&aacute;c s&aacute;ng ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200bxanh \u0111\u1ec3 c&oacute; m\u1ed9t m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 158px;top: 753.898px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-7jo6q60k{ padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 50px;}.ffb-id-7jo6q60u{ margin-right: 30px;margin-left: 30px;padding-top: 30px;padding-right: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}@media (min-width:768px) { .ffb-id-7jo6q60u{ margin-right: 30px;margin-left: 30px;padding-right: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}}@media (min-width:992px) { .ffb-id-7jo6q60u{ margin-right: 30px;margin-left: 30px;padding-right: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}}@media (min-width:1200px) { .ffb-id-7jo6q60u{ margin-right: 30px;margin-left: 30px;padding-right: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}}.ffb-id-7jo6q610{ padding-top: 10px;padding-right: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 10px;}.ffb-id-7jo6q610 ,.ffb-id-7jo6q610:before,.ffb-id-7jo6q610:after,.ffb-id-7jo6q610 *,.ffb-id-7jo6q610 *:before,.ffb-id-7jo6q610 *:after{ color: #797979 !important;}.ffb-id-7jo6q610{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-7jo6q610:before,.ffb-id-7jo6q610:after,.ffb-id-7jo6q610:hover,.ffb-id-7jo6q610:focus,.ffb-id-7jo6q610 *,.f